---
title: Sweet and Savoury Beef Burgers with Herby Fries and Dijonnaise
description: Everyone loves a good hamburger, but this one may just change the game! Maple and thyme make beef shine here, while ketchup and Dijonnaise act as major flavour boosters. Throw in a fresh apple-spinach salad and some herby potato wedges to satisfy that next burger craving!
